PrecisAuthority to execute an instrument intitled "Surrender of Lease" which provides for the surrender by the Crown of the leasehold interests it acquired by assignment in 1983 with respect to certain lands and premises (Hanger 1A) situate at Edmonton Municipal Airport, the demised premises in question having been subsequently leased to the Crown in 1986 under the terms of a new twenty-five (25) year lease.
